component.notes:
Address 1 = A - if A == 10 pl wins 0 before Address 2 = PL - if pl>9 A wins 0 before Address 3 = Interface - Put #4#0x where "x" means interface number and it can goes to 5. If Main Bus Instalation, leave it blank
L4686SDK need to be on 1.20 firmware version. See http://myrti.ru/index.php/l4686sdk-to-rs232/en/ to assemble your cable/adapter

action_argument.name: ShadeLevel
action_argument.note: Percentage to not be shaded. 0 means all the way down, 100 means all the way up
